{"tid":2510148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六四未經批准集結案 黃之鋒岑敖暉袁嘉蔚梁凱晴認罪 朱凱廸仍需時考慮答辯方向","createTime":"2021-04-30T03:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T03:23:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92a04087de5dcfc5291428ba5cb97091afeee49d","tid":2510148,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:00:44.000Z","msg":"去年警方禁止維園六四燭光集會，惟支聯會及大批市民堅持到維園紀念，其後支聯會主席李卓人、副主席何俊仁、多名常委以及壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英等24人被控煽惑他人參與未經批准集結罪，以及參與一個未經批准集結等罪。其中朱凱廸、黃之鋒、岑敖暉、袁嘉蔚及梁凱晴五人早前透過律師表示擬承認參與未經批准集結罪。區域法院法官陳廣池今開庭處理，其中四人維持認罪答辯，而朱凱廸則表示仍在考慮中。控方現向認罪四人讀出承認案情。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒、岑敖暉、袁嘉蔚及梁凱晴今早承認明知而參與未經批准集結罪。控方申請將四人的案件合併，獲法官批准。控方遂向四人讀出承認案情。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸則透過代表大狀表示，仍需時考慮是否認罪，要求將案件押後再訊。法官遂將朱的案件押後至6月11日，與其餘未認罪的被告一同再訊。朱因涉違反國安法，仍須繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸今早精神不俗，於被告欄內向觀眾席方向打眼色。代表朱的資深大律師夏偉志表示，朱仍然在考慮答辯方向，故申請押後案件，獲法官批准。散庭後，朱從被告欄走進羈留室，多名旁聽人士高呼：「撐住呀！」「我哋掛住你呀，廸！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/G7FBCZNJANDX5FVWDQ5QPJHBNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FG7FBCZNJANDX5FVWDQ5QPJHBNQ%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=df6d94a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FG7FBCZNJANDX5FVWDQ5QPJHBNQ%2F&h=1d0388c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/G7FBCZNJANDX5FVWDQ5QPJHBNQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ae8b342c333e058bdfc8a6bf840ceb8eda8813c0","tid":2510148,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15362&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=55f1e5c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15362</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅二庭 #英語聆訊<br />\n#陳廣池法官 #聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n👥梁凱睛,岑敖暉,黃之鋒,袁家蔚 #20200604維園<br />\n🛑岑敖暉,袁家蔚因另案而被還押逾1個月，黃之鋒因另案服刑中🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪：參與未經批准集結<br />\n4人被控於2020年6月4日，在香港維多利亞公園，連同同案其他被告及其他不詳人士，明知而參與未經批准集結。<br />\n===================<br />\n控方申請把案件合併，辯方沒有反對。<br />\n<br />\n‼️4人認罪‼️<br />\n<br />\n11:06 休庭至11:30"},{"pid":"00f7734a87f7c0aff18dca05b6c0865abbb72c5f","tid":2510148,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dc22354831bd2667e1e13e067530ac6870b9513","tid":2510148,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd9564a5be44c3828d54f30de80595e1c7de6fc","tid":2510148,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"無人再去六四集會 共產黨唔會仲驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a532a74f815e2dc9b233505563f25c1a9bb6179b","tid":2510148,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}